pod/releases/assets/333708945\",\n                \"id\": 333708945,\n                \"node_id\": \"RA_kwDOQvpNOc4T4_6R\",\n                \"name\": \"CodePod_aarch64.app.tar.gz\",\n                \"label\": \"\",\n                \"uploader\": {\n                    \"login\": \"github-actions[bot]\",\n                    \"id\": 41898282,\n                    \"node_id\": \"MDM6Qm90NDE4OTgyODI=\",\n                    \"avatar_url\": \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/in/15368?v=4\",\n                    \"gravatar_id\": \"\",\n                    \"url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D\",\n                    \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/apps/github-actions\",\n                    \"followers_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/followers\",\n                    \"following_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/following{/other_user}\",\n                    \"gists_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/gists{/gist_id}\",\n                    \"starred_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\n                    \"subscriptions_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/subscriptions\",\n                    \"organizations_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/orgs\",\n                    \"repos_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/repos\",\n                    \"events_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/events{/privacy}\",\n                    \"received_events_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/received_events\",\n                    \"type\": \"Bot\",\n                    \"user_view_type\": \"public\",\n                    \"site_admin\": false\n                },\n                \"content_type\": \"application/zip\",\n                \"state\": \"uploaded\",\n                \"size\": 4363432,\n                \"digest\": \"sha256:144204efe28388d80b38593751093497e58295d2c50ac830f6f98fdd3facc6db\",\n                \"download_count\": 7,\n                \"created_at\": \"2025-12-28T07:45:53Z\",\n                \"updated_at\": \"2025-12-28T07:45:54Z\",\n                \"browser_download_url\": \"https://github.com/chicogong/codepod/releases/download/v0.5.0/CodePod_aarch64.app.tar.gz\"\n            }\n        ],\n        \"tarball_url\": \"https://api.github.com/repos/chicogong/codepod/tarball/v0.5.0\",\n        \"zipball_url\": \"https://api.github.com/repos/chicogong/codepod/zipball/v0.5.0\",\n        \"body\": \"# CodePod v0.5.0\\n\\nA major update bringing terminal integration, UI enhancements, and multi-platform support.\\n\\n![CodePod Screenshot](https://github.com/chicogong/codepod/releases/download/v0.5.0/codepod-window.png)\\n\\n## \\ud83c\\udf89 What's New\\n\\n### \\ud83d\\udda5\\ufe0f Terminal Support\\n- **Full PTY Integration**: Interactive terminal sessions with Claude CLI\\n- **xterm.js Terminal Emulator**: Full-featured terminal with color support (xterm-256color)\\n- **Session Management**: Create, resume, and manage multiple terminal sessions\\n- **Real-time Bidirectional Communication**: Send input and receive output in real-time\\n- **Auto-resize**: Terminal automatically adapts to window size changes\\n- **Exit Code Display**: Clear indication when processes terminate\\n\\n### \\ud83c\\udfa8 Naive UI Integration\\n- **Modern Component Library**: Migrated to Naive UI for a polished, professional interface\\n- **Improved UX**: Better layout, spacing, and visual hierarchy\\n- **Responsive Design**: Optimized for different window sizes\\n- **Dark Mode**: Beautiful dark theme by default\\n\\n### \\ud83d\\udcd1 Advanced Features\\n- **Multi-Tab Support**: Work with multiple conversations simultaneously\\n- **Export Conversations**: Save chat history for later reference\\n- **Token Statistics**: Track input/output tokens and estimated costs\\n- **Session Persistence**: All conversations auto-saved to localStorage\\n- **Streaming Output**: Real-time message streaming for better responsiveness\\n\\n### \\ud83d\\udd27 Dual CLI Support\\n- **Claude & CodeBuddy**: Switch between `claude` and `codebuddy` CLI executables\\n- **Flexible Configuration**: Choose your preferred CLI tool in settings\\n\\n### \\ud83c\\udfaf Other Improvements\\n- **Model Selector**: Easy switching between Claude models (Sonnet, Opus, Haiku)\\n- **Improved Error Handling**: Better error messages and recovery\\n- **Code Highlighting**: Syntax highlighting with Shiki\\n- **Better Performance**: Optimized rendering and memory usage\\n\\n## \\ud83d\\udce6 Installation\\n\\n### macOS\\n- **Apple Silicon (M1/M2/M3)**: Download `CodePod_0.1.0_aarch64.dmg`\\n- **Alternative**: Use `CodePod_aarch64.app.tar.gz` for manual installation\\n\\n### Windows\\n- **Setup Installer**: Download `CodePod_0.1.0_x64-setup.exe` (recommended)\\n- **MSI Installer**: Download `CodePod_0.1.0_x64_en-US.msi`\\n\\n### Linux\\n- **AppImage** (Universal): Download `CodePod_0.1.0_amd64.AppImage`\\n- **Debian/Ubuntu**: Download `CodePod_0.1.0_amd64.deb`\\n- **Fedora/RHEL**: Download `CodePod-0.1.0-1.x86_64.rpm`\\n\\n## \\ud83d\\udd28 Technical Details\\n\\n### Architecture Changes\\n- **Package Manager**: Migrated from Bun to npm for better stability\\n- **Build System**: GitHub Actions workflow for automated multi-platform builds\\n- **TypeScript**: Full type safety across the codebase\\n- **Testing**: 113 passing tests with Vitest\\n\\n### Dependencies\\n- **Frontend**: Vue 3, Naive UI, Pinia, xterm.js\\n- **Backend**: Tauri v2, Rust with portable-pty\\n- **Bundler**: Vite\\n\\n## \\ud83d\\udcdd Notes\\n\\n- This release requires Claude CLI to be installed and accessible in your PATH\\n- Terminal feature requires `claude` or `codebuddy` CLI executable\\n- First-time users: Set your project path in settings for best experience\\n\\n## \\ud83d\\udc1b Bug Fixes\\n\\n- Fixed TypeScript compilation errors in session store\\n- Fixed undefined array access in terminal management\\n- Fixed build configuration for cross-platform compatibility\\n- Fixed GitHub Actions workflow for npm-based builds\\n\\n## \\ud83d\\ude4f Credits\\n\\nBuilt with \\u2764\\ufe0f using:\\n- [Tauri](https://tauri.app/) - Desktop app framework\\n- [Vue 3](https://vuejs.org/) - Frontend framework\\n- [Naive UI](https://www.naiveui.com/) - Component library\\n- [xterm.js](https://xtermjs.org/) - Terminal emulator\\n- [Claude](https://claude.ai/) - AI assistant\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/chicogong/codepod/compare/v0.4.0...v0.5.0\\n\"\n    }\n]","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"419fc3db-1979-4399-a159-b103ea140417","uuid":"4e881e3b-b049-4bf9-b894-5c76dda5023d","timestamp":"2026-05-21T18:30:28.918Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"[\n    {\n        \"url\": \"https://api.github.com/repos/chicogong/codepod/releases/273052198\",\n        \"assets_url\": \"https://api.github.com/repos/chicogong/codepod/releases/273052198/assets\",\n        \"upload_url\": \"https://uploads.github.com/repos/chicogong/codepod/releases/273052198/assets{?name,label}\",\n        \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/chicogong/codepod/releases/tag/v0.5.0\",\n        \"id\": 273052198,\n        \"author\": {\n            \"login\": \"github-actions[bot]\",\n            \"id\": 41898282,\n            \"node_id\": \"MDM6Qm90NDE4OTgyODI=\",\n            \"avatar_url\": \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/in/15368?v=4\",\n            \"gravatar_id\": \"\",\n            \"url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D\",\n            \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/apps/github-actions\",\n            \"followers_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/followers\",\n            \"following_url\": \"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/following{/other_user}\",\n            \"gi